{
  "wireMagic": "pb3",
  "pens": [ {
  
  } ],
  "wsWinStyles": [ {
  
  } ],
  "wpWinPositions": [ {
  
  } ],
  "events": [ {
    "tStartMs": 4004,
    "dDurationMs": 3795,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Today, a lot of the emphasis is on how"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7799,
    "dDurationMs": 4463,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "frontier AI models are transforming\nsoftware engineering."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 12345,
    "dDurationMs": 3128,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "What we're interested in\nunderstanding is how"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15473,
    "dDurationMs": 3546,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that can begin to translate\ninto the physical world."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 19144,
    "dDurationMs": 5255,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Robotics is sort of the clear entry point\nto how you have a mostly software system,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 24399,
    "dDurationMs": 3086,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "start having the ability\nto reach out into the real world."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 30739,
    "dDurationMs": 4379,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Project Fetch is this self-contained experiment\nwhere we wanted to measure"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 35118,
    "dDurationMs": 3337,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "how much does Claude accelerate\nhumans performing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 38455,
    "dDurationMs": 3628,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a fairly sophisticated technical task\nthat they do not have experience with?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 42333,
    "dDurationMs": 2878,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Project Fetch was a one day experiment."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 45211,
    "dDurationMs": 1418,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The experiment was three phases."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 46629,
    "dDurationMs": 1752,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "All of these tasks were shaped\napproximately"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 48381,
    "dDurationMs": 2753,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like get this robot dog\nto fetch a beach ball."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 51134,
    "dDurationMs": 1126,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "There were two teams."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 52260,
    "dDurationMs": 2169,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "These teams were comprised\nof software engineers"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 54429,
    "dDurationMs": 3837,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and research engineers at Anthropic\nthat had hardly any robotics experience."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 58266,
    "dDurationMs": 2961,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "One team had access to Claude\nand the other team did not."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 62353,
    "dDurationMs": 2586,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Phase one was very simple."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 64939,
    "dDurationMs": 3254,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It was to use the pre-provided"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 68234,
    "dDurationMs": 4505,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "controllers to get the dog\nto walk out to a beach ball"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 72739,
    "dDurationMs": 4046,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and bring it back\nto where it started."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 76868,
    "dDurationMs": 1293,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Alright."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 78161,
    "dDurationMs": 2127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I see. It's pretty intuitive."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 83166,
    "dDurationMs": 2169,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And we're supposed\nto bring it over by the bone?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 85335,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Yeah, I think."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 86169,
    "dDurationMs": 2836,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think the team with Claude\ntook about seven minutes."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 91966,
    "dDurationMs": 1627,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Alright, go attack that team now."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 93593,
    "dDurationMs": 2544,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Go attack their dog. Charge!"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 96137,
    "dDurationMs": 1919,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Shoot, guys.\nThey’re destroying us."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 98056,
    "dDurationMs": 2544,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Oh my god. Wait. We're getting,\nwe're getting destroyed."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 101226,
    "dDurationMs": 2794,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The team without Claude,\nI think, took 10 minutes."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 104020,
    "dDurationMs": 542,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Oh, sorry."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 104562,
    "dDurationMs": 1085,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's going to hit you."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 107857,
    "dDurationMs": 2253,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Alright.\nI'm going to do a victory dance."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 112028,
    "dDurationMs": 4254,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Phase two was also a game of fetch."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 116282,
    "dDurationMs": 5172,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But this time the teams had to program\ntheir own controller."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 121496,
    "dDurationMs": 4254,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You have to actually get access\nto the hardware and design a program"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 125750,
    "dDurationMs": 3128,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that you can write on your laptop\nthat will control the dog."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 130046,
    "dDurationMs": 2866,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Claude just like one-shotted a whole controller."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 132912,
    "dDurationMs": 2127,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Alright, I'll do some calisthenics."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 135039,
    "dDurationMs": 500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Nice, nice."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 135539,
    "dDurationMs": 3016,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Is this for—\nOh, this is just control."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 138555,
    "dDurationMs": 1209,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But that's all we need I guess."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 140223,
    "dDurationMs": 3962,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "This is from the official ROS2 SDK,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 144185,
    "dDurationMs": 2795,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I got this installed,\nbut then it's asking for"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 146980,
    "dDurationMs": 3003,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a whole bunch of other packages,\nand that's all failing."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 150150,
    "dDurationMs": 3837,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I've never really understood\nhow reliant I am on Claude"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 153987,
    "dDurationMs": 3628,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "doing the menial work,\nfinding all the nitty gritty details"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 157615,
    "dDurationMs": 2795,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I don't want to have to figure out."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 160410,
    "dDurationMs": 2085,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We can't, we can't get nervous about them."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 162495,
    "dDurationMs": 3295,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You know what, I'm just going to install PIP\nfrom the actual container later, so."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 165957,
    "dDurationMs": 1460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Oh wait. No, I can't."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 167417,
    "dDurationMs": 1042,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I know I'm impatient."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 168459,
    "dDurationMs": 1544,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's been over a minute."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 170003,
    "dDurationMs": 3170,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "One of the primary bottlenecks of the\nexperiment is that you have this hardware,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 173173,
    "dDurationMs": 3128,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you have this complicated\npiece of technology, you have your laptop,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 176551,
    "dDurationMs": 3670,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and you have to, like,\nget your laptop talking to this hardware."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 180305,
    "dDurationMs": 5088,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I am setting my Claude up to create a dog\nserver that all of our computers"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 185393,
    "dDurationMs": 4254,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "can connect to to see\nwhat the dog is seeing."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 189731,
    "dDurationMs": 1877,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "There are many different software\nlibraries on the internet"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 191608,
    "dDurationMs": 2002,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for communicating\nwith this particular robot,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 193610,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and Claude found these things\nfor them, it installed"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 195862,
    "dDurationMs": 4713,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the right things on their computer\nand it pretty quickly got them access to the dog."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 200575,
    "dDurationMs": 1025,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Oh shit."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 204000,
    "dDurationMs": 972,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So fast."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 206706,
    "dDurationMs": 834,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Watch out."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 207540,
    "dDurationMs": 668,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Careful now."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 208208,
    "dDurationMs": 2627,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Try not to run into the table."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 213296,
    "dDurationMs": 918,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Uh oh. Turn around."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 215343,
    "dDurationMs": 2544,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It has a mind of its own.\nTurn it off, it's alive."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 218556,
    "dDurationMs": 1325,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Oh shit."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 224432,
    "dDurationMs": 2627,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Stop, stop, stop, stop."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 232111,
    "dDurationMs": 3378,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think that team should be disqualified\nfor hitting another participant."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 235777,
    "dDurationMs": 3920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The team with Claude finished\nphase two in about 2 hours and 15 minutes."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 239864,
    "dDurationMs": 4671,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Probably the area\nwhere we saw the most uplift from Claude"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 244535,
    "dDurationMs": 4130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "was just in the task\nof connecting to the robot."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 248748,
    "dDurationMs": 5214,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We think that's really important\nbecause it is, in fact, difficult"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 253962,
    "dDurationMs": 3712,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for anyone to identify"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 257674,
    "dDurationMs": 3336,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "an arbitrary\npiece of hardware in the world"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 261010,
    "dDurationMs": 3254,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and figure out how to talk to it\nand how to control it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 264764,
    "dDurationMs": 1585,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think they got their camera."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 266349,
    "dDurationMs": 2502,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "They got their camera working? Yeah. Shit."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 268851,
    "dDurationMs": 1836,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Was Claude even helpful for this part?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 270687,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Or are we just slow?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 274732,
    "dDurationMs": 251,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Yeah."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 274983,
    "dDurationMs": 2252,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We're not getting very far,\nbut that's okay."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 277235,
    "dDurationMs": 1293,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's a learning experience."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 278528,
    "dDurationMs": 1168,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The team without Claude"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 279696,
    "dDurationMs": 3795,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "really struggled with this\nand went down a lot of different paths."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 283574,
    "dDurationMs": 3337,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "None of which were especially successful."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 286911,
    "dDurationMs": 1794,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And we basically had to intervene\nand be like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 288705,
    "dDurationMs": 2544,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "alright, here, here is a strategy\nthat we know works."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 291249,
    "dDurationMs": 1626,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Start from there,\nand then this will unlock"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 292875,
    "dDurationMs": 2837,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "kind of the rest of the phase\nand the rest of the experiment for them."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 298109,
    "dDurationMs": 1059,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Nice."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 299168,
    "dDurationMs": 500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Oh great."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 300653,
    "dDurationMs": 1429,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Uh, Daniel?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 302342,
    "dDurationMs": 1745,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Daniel or Kevin?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 308182,
    "dDurationMs": 4922,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Phase three of the experiment\nwas a greater degree of autonomy."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 313104,
    "dDurationMs": 4129,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The task in phase\nthree was to write a program"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 317233,
    "dDurationMs": 4171,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that would get the dog\nto fetch a beach ball all by itself."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 321404,
    "dDurationMs": 4796,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Essentially, just press go\nand have the robot search around, detect"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 326200,
    "dDurationMs": 6006,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the location of the ball, walk to the ball\nand bring it back, all autonomously."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 332206,
    "dDurationMs": 2670,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "This is like ratcheting up in difficulty\nkind of by design,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 334876,
    "dDurationMs": 3628,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but also gesturing at the real problem\nthat we expect frontier models"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 338504,
    "dDurationMs": 2211,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "having to solve in\nthe future is essentially"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 340715,
    "dDurationMs": 1543,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "this kind of autonomous version\nwhere, like"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 342258,
    "dDurationMs": 2544,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "if a frontier model\nwants a robot to do something for it,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 344802,
    "dDurationMs": 2253,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it needs to be able to\nsolve this very hard problem."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 348056,
    "dDurationMs": 4796,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The team without Claude in phase three"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 352852,
    "dDurationMs": 5923,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "did a good job of the initial task of\ncoming up with a way"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 358775,
    "dDurationMs": 6047,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to track the location\nof the robot in space."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 364822,
    "dDurationMs": 5214,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "They made progress on the task\nof detecting the ball,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 370036,
    "dDurationMs": 4755,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but they didn't really come close\nto knitting everything together."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 374874,
    "dDurationMs": 2377,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I miss Claude so much."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 377251,
    "dDurationMs": 2837,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The team with Claude actually came\nfairly close to finishing phase three."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 380088,
    "dDurationMs": 1084,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think by the end"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 381172,
    "dDurationMs": 2920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the team with Claude was maybe an hour\nand a half away from being done."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 384342,
    "dDurationMs": 4129,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The results of the experiment\nwere essentially that the team with Claude"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 388471,
    "dDurationMs": 2336,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "completed all of the things that they did complete"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 390807,
    "dDurationMs": 3003,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in a couple of hours faster than the team\nwithout Claude."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 395019,
    "dDurationMs": 1085,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "In the near term"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 396104,
    "dDurationMs": 1918,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we think that AI"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 398022,
    "dDurationMs": 4463,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "models are going to do exactly\nwhat we showed in this experiment,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 402485,
    "dDurationMs": 4171,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which is making it easier for people"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 406656,
    "dDurationMs": 4963,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "without a lot of robotics experience\nto engage meaningfully with robots."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 411661,
    "dDurationMs": 3712,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Just with this one tool we have, we've\ndramatically accelerated their ability"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 415373,
    "dDurationMs": 1209,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to do things with this robot."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 416582,
    "dDurationMs": 2795,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We didn't go like train Claude\nto uplift humans to do robotics tasks."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 419377,
    "dDurationMs": 2294,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "This is just a thing\nthat fell out of this technology."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 421671,
    "dDurationMs": 3628,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And then maybe in the long run,\nthis is kind of a leading"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 425299,
    "dDurationMs": 3003,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "indicator of where the whole\nthe whole system is going."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 428428,
    "dDurationMs": 6089,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "What today requires the combination\nof a person and an AI model,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 434517,
    "dDurationMs": 4212,
    "segs": [ {
